text: "Gump" is a song by "Weird Al" Yankovic. It is a parody of "Lump" by The Presidents of the United States of America. It was released on the album Bad Hair Day in 1996. The song is a humorous retelling of the movie Forrest Gump. Category:"Weird Al" Yankovic songs Category:Parodies Category:1996 songs
title: Gump (song)
